list/zVctGZ8uky1R" target="_blank" rel="noopener">的电影排名</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/all-of-us-strangers-review-paul-mescal-andrew-scott-claire-foy-3576917">《我们都是陌生人》评论：今年最悲伤的电影</a></strong></li></ul><p>该列表是根据流行电影官方讨论论坛上附加的民意调查评级生成的。用户可以对他们看过的电影从十分之一进行评分，并投票决定是否推荐这些电影。</p><p>前十名的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2024-nominations-rolling-list-3575357">奥斯卡提名影片</a>包括平均分8.65的<em>《保留</em>》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/past-lives-review-a24-greta-lee-3495175"><em>《前世》</em></a>和<em>《兴趣地带》</em> 。<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-concert-movie-3513715"><em>Taylor Swift: The Eras Tour</em></a>在前 20 名榜单中稳坐第 11 位，平均评分为 8.38。</p><p>排名中还包括动画和奇幻电影，其中<em>《蜘蛛侠：穿越蜘蛛侠宇宙》</em>以平均分 9.18 分排名第一， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/guardians-of-the-galaxy-volume-3-review-james-gunn-3437058"><em>《银河护卫队 3》</em></a>排名第 17。 </p><figure id="attachment_3579471" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3579471" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3579471" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/society-of-the-snow-reddit.jpg" alt="雪之协会" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/society-of-the-snow-reddit.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/society-of-the-snow-reddit-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/society-of-the-snow-reddit-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/society-of-the-snow-reddit-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/society-of-the-snow-reddit-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/society-of-the-snow-reddit-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3579471" class="wp-caption-text"> 《雪之社会》位居第二。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>一些相对较新的电影也进入了2023年电影排行榜。 2 月 9 日才在英国上映的<em>《铁爪》</em>排名第八，而最近上映的<em>《我们陌生人》</em>则以 8.64 的平均收视率排名第六。</p><p>查看下面的完整列表。</p><ol><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>蜘蛛侠：穿越蜘蛛侠宇宙</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>雪之协会</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>哥斯拉减一</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>文艺复兴：<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a>的电影</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>保留的东西</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>我们都是陌生人</em></li><li aria-level="1"><em>尼莫娜</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>铁爪</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>前世</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>油布</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>：时代巡演</em></li><li aria-level="1"><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>奥本海默</em></a></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>他们克隆了泰隆</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>神你在吗？是我，玛格丽特。</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>黑莓</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>经纪人</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>银河护卫队 Vol.3</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>龙与地下城：盗贼的荣耀</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><em>跌倒的解剖</em></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/john-wick-chapter-4-review-keanu-reeves-3418262"><em>约翰威克：第 4 章</em></a></li></ol><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/reddit-favourite-movies-of-2023-3579464">《这些是去年 Reddit 最喜欢的电影》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
